Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Reagan's Europe tour
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043wvmw
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 6 Jun 1982
President Reagan prepares for Europe grand tour aimed at polishing his image abroad. The sound quality on this recording is variable/poor. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less